{"tid":1726623,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《區選建議》希望泛民區選手足可以入一入黎睇","createTime":"2019-11-16T08:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T10:50:15.000Z","uid":112205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"13927d236671dbcafeda4f0a430b00f5df3f42d3","tid":1726623,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:35:28.000Z","msg":"區選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">藍色的人會投藍色，黃色的人會投黃色</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">咁泛民侯選者仲可以做咩？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為一個係建制派區生存多年的老街坊，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我的建議係用感情牌拉中間選民</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，雖然社會打得難分難解，但確實有一部份人係活在平衡時空。中間派的選民記並不是以政治議題為考慮條件，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">而是考慮侯選人的個人表現，包括親和力、感情渲染力、社區關係、社區問題及社區回憶。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見到有手足用政治批判的角度大大力出發，但講左15分鐘都冇人聽。不妨用唔同角度去游說區民投一票比你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但當然，其他手足可以帶藍絲父母去旅行、食齋、返大陸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdea1a9915c8a0f4f4f0ea939181dc0bb5005125","tid":1726623,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13927d236671dbcafeda4f0a430b00f5df3f42d3","tid":1726623,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:35:28.000Z","msg":"區選<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">藍色的人會投藍色，黃色的人會投黃色</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">咁泛民侯選者仲可以做咩？</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n作為一個係建制派區生存多年的老街坊，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我的建議係用感情牌拉中間選民</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上，雖然社會打得難分難解，但確實有一部份人係活在平衡時空。中間派的選民記並不是以政治議題為考慮條件，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">而是考慮侯選人的個人表現，包括親和力、感情渲染力、社區關係、社區問題及社區回憶。</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我見到有手足用政治批判的角度大大力出發，但講左15分鐘都冇人聽。不妨用唔同角度去游說區民投一票比你。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但當然，其他手足可以帶藍絲父母去旅行、食齋、返大陸。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:36:20.000Z","msg":"區選當日 以1換2"},{"pid":"7efbf1ae37f2b3919d76cd5e7da866327e3f7355","tid":1726623,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:36:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d72e024b38714936dd44216d654e44530df8d658","tid":1726623,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:38:48.000Z","msg":"小小建議 希望幫到手<br />\n<br />\n未必要大大力標明自己係黃<br />\n<br />\n一兩個位知你係同路人 黃色既會投比你<br />\n<br />\n反而係拉中間派都係著眼點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"815bf20892b5f0a195cd7cb5da939ae20f1f1688","tid":1726623,"uid":112205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T08:39:48.000Z","msg":"推到比區